Class ParserProfileChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.riot.system.ParserProfileBase
      • org.apache.jena.riot.system.ParserProfileChecker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserProfile

    public class ParserProfileChecker
extends ParserProfileBase
    ParserProfile that performs checks:
    • IRI violations
    • Valid lexical forms for literals
    • Valid triples (e.g. literals as subjects)
    • Valid quads
